channel.title: What the fuck does this mean?
channel.description:
What the fuck does my poem mean?
Open that door and draw you in time for quick and stupid sin, close the mind and harden heart shut me up before I start, cruel and callow quick and leering never know what we're fearing, inhale exhale gray and pale never let my cruelty fail, floating high and aiming low never one to take it slow, now the change just drop the wall look at you and watch it fall hopeless fantasy of this young boy, you are just my nightmare toy.
???

About smoking something. Just a quick joint?

time for quick and stupid sin
Quick little joint? Stupid as in "this isn't really a bad thing, how is it a sin?"
inhale exhale gray and pale
Dur.
floating high and aiming low
High on whatever you're smoking, but aiming low in life.

Etc.

Like I said, smoking pot or something of a sort is my guess…
Don’t really want to “analyze” it.

-Mh
